                                <td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=28314&amp;sid=a89249cc9b56b6a633b8a8cdd519a772#28314"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed Mar 03, 2004 8:07 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Approach to choosing AA</span></td>
                                <td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=28314&amp;sid=a89249cc9b56b6a633b8a8cdd519a772"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>    </td>
