                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you don't have Eldrich Rune yet, get it. Can't stress this ability enough.
<br />

<br />
MC3 and Gather Mana should be your next step after that.
<br />

<br />
That takes care of Survival and Mana more or less.
<br />

<br />
As for DPS, we suck at it. If you have Insanity, you nukes aren't going to get much better even if you invest in Crit AAs. About 1/100 chance that you will get one when you need, and if it isnt resisted.
<br />

<br />
Getting Natural Durability and Combat Agility/Lightning Reflexes is another good step, but would also put a few in Spell Casting Subtlety.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=273350" target="_blank" class="postlink">Mistress Senilea Starbreeze</a>
<br />
65 Coercer of Bristlebane
