<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
This ignores one (IMO, very important) thing; ER is only usable every 10 minutes.  AR is usable over and over again, as long as I've got mana.  Given the option, having both available is great (and will save a lot of mana for those occasions when you don't need to be chaining it), but AR-tanking (often hard-hitting) slowed mobs has saved me and my groups enough that I don't regret for a second getting QB3 before ER.
<br />

<br />
That said, ER is near the top of my list once I finish saving up for Mez Mastery...</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Sage Velurian Soliqui, E'ci
